<br>
I myself never understood why pets dont sclae with the level of the caster. Because I find it logical that my pet gets better when I am growing in power. Why have a random lvl pet summon. Why not just add a level each lvl the caster levels. Then casters would also not have that much problem in before &quot;new spell circle levels&quot;.<br>
<br>
Now pets resists scale with the power of the caster. GREAT IDEA !!! It should be like this with other stats also.<br>
<br>
I am all for this idea. Pets need to scale up in power when the caster lvl increases and maybe scale up when the stats of the caster increases like with resists. It could also be done by the implementation of pet foci. And different ones. That would  again add to the versatility to our pets.<br>
<br>
